title: Dortmund's Title Challenge Begins?
description:
The FC crew react to Borussia Dortmund's come from behind draw against Bayern Munich and question if this is finally the season we see Dortmund challenge for the title. Plus, Erling Haaland continues his scoring streak and AC Milan bounce back from a midweek defeat to breeze past Juventus 2-0.
